Enable color stripping so that regexes for commands don't need to handle it. ex. "bot: he^C2^Olp" still matches help regex despite invisible characters. This is useful if you use hubot with bitlbee to connect to AIM, MSN, YM etc with OTR, since bitlbee OTR makes text red when it's encrypted.
